readJsonFile

public String readJsonFile(String filePath)
Read JSON file to memory

参数：
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type
返回：
the content of the JSON file in String type

writeJsonFile

public void writeJsonFile(String jsonString,
                          String filePath)
Write the JSON file in memory to disk

参数：
jsonString - the content of the JSON file in String type
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type

ls

public void ls(String filePath,
               Type mapType,
               int directoryIndex,
               ArrayList resultArray)
ls command to list the items in current position

参数：
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type
mapType - the map type of the JSON file
directoryIndex - the current position of directory in JSON file
resultArray - the ArrayList contains the files in this directory

cd

public int cd(int directoryIndex,
              String[] commands)
cd command to go to the entry like go to a directory

参数：
directoryIndex - the current position of directory in JSON file
commands - the commands content in String array
返回：
-1 : error signal, execute fail directoryIndex : new directory position

cat

public String cat(String filePath,
                  Type mapType,
                  String mapKey,
                  String nameKey)
cat command to display th item data

参数：
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type
mapType - the map type of the JSON file
mapKey - the key of the map of the JSON file
nameKey - the name of the item
返回：
the content item data in string type, if no such item, return the error message

add

public String add(String filePath,
                  Type mapType,
                  String mapKey,
                  String name,
                  String value,
                  Type valueType)
add command to add new address entry to JSON

参数：
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type
mapType - the map type of the JSON file
mapKey - the key of the map of the JSON file
name - the name of the new address entry
value - the age, mobile, address information of the new address entry
valueType - the map type of the value information
返回：
if trying to add duplicated key, return an error message, otherwise return "address entry added"

remove

public String remove(String filePath,
                     Type mapType,
                     String mapKey,
                     String nameKey)
remove command to remove one or more address entries

参数：
filePath - the disk position of JSON file in String type
mapType - the map type of the JSON file
mapKey - the key of the map of the JSON file
nameKey - the name of the new address entry
返回：
if no such item, return the error message, otherwise return the correct prompt
